*Piter* je bio vrlo uspešan. (Peter was very successful.)
Oni su bili na *piter*u. (They were on a spree.)
Oni su se smejali *piteru*. (They were laughing at Peter.)
Ona je dala *Piteru* odgovor. (She gave Peter an answer.)
Niko nije znao *piter*u. (Nobody knew Peter.)
On je čuo *Pitera* kako govori. (He heard Peter talking.)
Ona je voljela *Pitera*. (She loved Peter.)